('abc09743-c27f-4207-b634-ab78041b2dbf', '{"en":"GATE PRACTICE","pa":"ਗੇਟ ਪ੍ਰੈਕਟਿਸ ਟੈਸਟ"}', '{"en":"FOR CS PART","pa":"ਕੰਪਿਊਟਰ ਸਾਇੰਸ ਪਾਰਟ"}', 180, 206, 40, NULL, TRUE, 'after_submit', 'draft', '18ab2fd0-7503-457a-8ba4-d04645052a9b', '"2026-02-10T02:02:48.796Z"', '"2026-02-14T11:00:21.522Z"', '{"en":"<h3><strong>GATE&nbsp;2025&nbsp;Exam&nbsp;Instructions</strong></h3><ol><li><strong>Exam&nbsp;Structure:</strong><ul><li><strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;3&nbsp;hours&nbsp;(180&nbsp;minutes).</li><li><strong>Total&nbsp;Marks:</strong>&nbsp;100&nbsp;marks.</li><li><strong>Total&nbsp;Questions:</strong>&nbsp;65&nbsp;questions.</li><li><strong>Sections:</strong><ul><li><strong>General&nbsp;Aptitude&nbsp;(GA):</strong>&nbsp;10&nbsp;questions&nbsp;(15&nbsp;marks&nbsp;total).&nbsp;This&nbsp;section&nbsp;is&nbsp;common&nbsp;for&nbsp;all&nbsp;papers.</li><li><strong>Computer&nbsp;Science&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Information&nbsp;Technology&nbsp;(CS):</strong>&nbsp;55&nbsp;questions&nbsp;(85&nbsp;marks&nbsp;total),&nbsp;including&nbsp;Engineering&nbsp;Mathematics.</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><strong>Question&nbsp;Types:</strong><ul><li><strong>Multiple&nbsp;Choice&nbsp;Questions&nbsp;(MCQ):</strong>&nbsp;Four&nbsp;options&nbsp;provided,&nbsp;only&nbsp;one&nbsp;correct.</li><li><strong>Multiple&nbsp;Select&nbsp;Questions&nbsp;(MSQ):</strong>&nbsp;Four&nbsp;options&nbsp;provided,&nbsp;one&nbsp;or&nbsp;more&nbsp;can&nbsp;be&nbsp;correct.&nbsp;All&nbsp;correct&nbsp;options&nbsp;must&nbsp;be&nbsp;selected&nbsp;for&nbsp;marks.&nbsp;No&nbsp;partial&nbsp;credit.</li><li><strong>Numerical&nbsp;Answer&nbsp;Type&nbsp;(NAT):</strong>&nbsp;No&nbsp;options&nbsp;provided.&nbsp;A&nbsp;numerical&nbsp;value&nbsp;must&nbsp;be&nbsp;entered&nbsp;using&nbsp;the&nbsp;virtual&nbsp;keypad.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Marking&nbsp;Scheme&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Negative&nbsp;Marking:</strong><ul><li><strong>1-Mark&nbsp;Questions:</strong><ul><li><strong>Correct:</strong>&nbsp;+1&nbsp;mark.</li><li><strong>Incorrect&nbsp;(MCQ):</strong>&nbsp;-1/3&nbsp;(approx.&nbsp;-0.33)&nbsp;marks.</li></ul></li><li><strong>2-Mark&nbsp;Questions:</strong><ul><li><strong>Correct:</strong>&nbsp;+2&nbsp;marks.</li><li><strong>Incorrect&nbsp;(MCQ):</strong>&nbsp;-2/3&nbsp;(approx.&nbsp;-0.66)&nbsp;marks.</li></ul></li><li><strong>No&nbsp;Negative&nbsp;Marking:</strong>&nbsp;There&nbsp;is&nbsp;<strong>NO</strong>&nbsp;negative&nbsp;marking&nbsp;for&nbsp;MSQ&nbsp;and&nbsp;NAT&nbsp;questions.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Exam&nbsp;Day&nbsp;Guidelines:</strong><ul><li><strong>Admit&nbsp;Card:</strong>&nbsp;Candidates&nbsp;must&nbsp;carry&nbsp;a&nbsp;printed&nbsp;hard&nbsp;copy&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;Admit&nbsp;Card.</li><li><strong>ID&nbsp;Proof:</strong>&nbsp;A&nbsp;valid&nbsp;original&nbsp;photo&nbsp;ID&nbsp;(Aadhaar,&nbsp;Passport,&nbsp;PAN&nbsp;Card,&nbsp;etc.)&nbsp;is&nbsp;mandatory.</li><li><strong>Prohibited&nbsp;Items:</strong>&nbsp;Electronic&nbsp;devices&nbsp;(phones,&nbsp;watches,&nbsp;calculators),&nbsp;bags,&nbsp;and&nbsp;other&nbsp;personal&nbsp;items&nbsp;are&nbsp;not&nbsp;allowed.</li><li><strong>Calculator:</strong>&nbsp;A&nbsp;virtual&nbsp;scientific&nbsp;calculator&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;available&nbsp;on&nbsp;the&nbsp;screen.&nbsp;Physical&nbsp;calculators&nbsp;are&nbsp;strictly&nbsp;prohibited.</li><li><strong>Rough&nbsp;Work:</strong>&nbsp;Scribble&nbsp;pads&nbsp;will&nbsp;be&nbsp;provided&nbsp;for&nbsp;rough&nbsp;work.&nbsp;These&nbsp;must&nbsp;be&nbsp;returned&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;end&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;exam.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Reporting&nbsp;Time:</strong><ul><li>Reach&nbsp;the&nbsp;center&nbsp;well&nbsp;in&nbsp;advance&nbsp;(at&nbsp;least&nbsp;60-90&nbsp;minutes&nbsp;early)&nbsp;to&nbsp;complete&nbsp;verification&nbsp;processes.</li><li>Late&nbsp;entry&nbsp;is&nbsp;generally&nbsp;not&nbsp;permitted&nbsp;after&nbsp;30&nbsp;minutes&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;start&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;exam.</li></ul></li></ol><p></p>","pa":"<h3><strong>GATE&nbsp;2025&nbsp;Exam&nbsp;Instructions</strong></h3><ol><li><strong>Exam&nbsp;Structure:</strong><ul><li><strong>Duration:</strong>&nbsp;3&nbsp;hours&nbsp;(180&nbsp;minutes).</li><li><strong>Total&nbsp;Marks:</strong>&nbsp;100&nbsp;marks.</li><li><strong>Total&nbsp;Questions:</strong>&nbsp;65&nbsp;questions.</li><li><strong>Sections:</strong><ul><li><strong>General&nbsp;Aptitude&nbsp;(GA):</strong>&nbsp;10&nbsp;questions&nbsp;(15&nbsp;marks&nbsp;total).&nbsp;This&nbsp;section&nbsp;is&nbsp;common&nbsp;for&nbsp;all&nbsp;papers.</li><li><strong>Computer&nbsp;Science&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Information&nbsp;Technology&nbsp;(CS):</strong>&nbsp;55&nbsp;questions&nbsp;(85&nbsp;marks&nbsp;total),&nbsp;including&nbsp;Engineering&nbsp;Mathematics.</li></ul></li></ul></li><li><strong>Question&nbsp;Types:</strong><ul><li><strong>Multiple&nbsp;Choice&nbsp;Questions&nbsp;(MCQ):</strong>&nbsp;Four&nbsp;options&nbsp;provided,&nbsp;only&nbsp;one&nbsp;correct.</li><li><strong>Multiple&nbsp;Select&nbsp;Questions&nbsp;(MSQ):</strong>&nbsp;Four&nbsp;options&nbsp;provided,&nbsp;one&nbsp;or&nbsp;more&nbsp;can&nbsp;be&nbsp;correct.&nbsp;All&nbsp;correct&nbsp;options&nbsp;must&nbsp;be&nbsp;selected&nbsp;for&nbsp;marks.&nbsp;No&nbsp;partial&nbsp;credit.</li><li><strong>Numerical&nbsp;Answer&nbsp;Type&nbsp;(NAT):</strong>&nbsp;No&nbsp;options&nbsp;provided.&nbsp;A&nbsp;numerical&nbsp;value&nbsp;must&nbsp;be&nbsp;entered&nbsp;using&nbsp;the&nbsp;virtual&nbsp;keypad.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Marking&nbsp;Scheme&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;Negative&nbsp;Marking:</strong><ul><li><strong>1-Mark&nbsp;Questions:</strong><ul><li><strong>Correct:</strong>&nbsp;+1&nbsp;mark.</li><li><strong>Incorrect&nbsp;(MCQ):</strong>&nbsp;-1/3&nbsp;(approx.&nbsp;-0.33)&nbsp;marks.</li></ul></li><li><strong>2-Mark&nbsp;Questions:</strong><ul><li><strong>Correct:</strong>&nbsp;+2&nbsp;marks.</li><li><strong>Incorrect&nbsp;(MCQ):</strong>&nbsp;-2/3&nbsp;(approx.&nbsp;-0.66)&nbsp;marks.</li></ul></li><li><strong>No&nbsp;Negative&nbsp;Marking:</strong>&nbsp;There&nbsp;is&nbsp;<s