('58770ec4-57f1-4255-8ccc-44f0347c1733', 'f4d9390b-b4a5-4387-b1d8-5a033627b550', 'mcq_single', '{"en":"Which of the following is true?","pa":"ਹੇਠ ਲਿਖੇ ਵਿੱਚੋਂ ਕਿਹੜਾ ਸਹੀ ਹੈ ?"}', '[{"id":"a","text":{"en":"sin²θ + tan²(90°-θ) = 1","pa":"sin²θ + tan²(90°-θ) = 1"}},{"id":"b","text":{"en":"cos²θ + cos²(90°-θ) = 1","pa":"cos²θ + cos²(90°-θ) = 1"}},{"id":"c","text":{"en":"sin²θ + cos²θ = 0","pa":"sin²θ + cos²θ = 0"}},{"id":"d","text":{"en":"sec²θ - sec²(90°-θ) = 1","pa":"sec²θ - sec²(90°-θ) = 1"}}]', '["b"]', '{"en":"cos²(90°-θ) = sin²θ. So cos²θ + sin²θ = 1, which is a standard identity.","pa":"cos²(90°-θ) = sin²θ. ਇਸ ਲਈ cos²θ + sin²θ = 1, ਜੋ ਕਿ ਇੱਕ ਮਿਆਰੀ ਪਛਾਣ ਹੈ।"}', 1, '0.00', NULL, 17, NULL, NULL, 4, NULL, '"2026-02-14T10:57:16.270Z"', '"2026-02-14T10:57:16.270Z"'),
('9d25fb81-1866-401c-96cb-c57b59cceef0', 'f4d9390b-b4a5-4387-b1d8-5a033627b550', 'mcq_single', '{"en":"If roots of a quadratic equation are 4 and -3, then the quadratic equation is:","pa":"ਜੇਕਰ ਇੱਕ ਦੋ ਘਾਤੀ ਸਮੀਕਰਣ ਦੇ ਮੂਲ 4 ਅਤੇ -3 ਹਨ ਤਾਂ ਦੋ ਘਾਤੀ ਸਮੀਕਰਣ ਹੈ :"}', '[{"id":"a","text":{"en":"x² - x - 12 = 0","pa":"x² - x - 12 = 0"}},{"id":"b","text":{"en":"x² + x - 12 = 0","pa":"x² + x - 12 = 0"}},{"id":"c","text":{"en":"x² + 7x - 12 = 0","pa":"x² + 7x - 12 = 0"}},{"id":"d","text":{"en":"x² - 7x + 12 = 0","pa":"x² - 7x + 12 = 0"}}]', '["a"]', '{"en":"Sum of roots = 4 + (-3) = 1. Product = 4 * (-3) = -12. Eq: x² - (sum)x + product = 0 => x² - x - 12 = 0.","pa":"ਮੂਲ ਦਾ ਜੋੜ = 1. ਗੁਣਨਫਲ = -12. ਸਮੀਕਰਣ: x² - (ਜੋੜ)x + ਗੁਣਨਫਲ = 0 => x² - x - 12 = 0."}', 1, '0.00', NULL, 22, NULL, NULL, 2, NULL, '"2026-02-14T10:57:16.270Z"', '"2026-02-14T10:57:16.270Z"'),
('9fbd2cee-71ec-4c34-9b76-d202b36984e2', 'f4d9390b-b4a5-4387-b1d8-5a033627b550', 'mcq_single', '{"en":"If ''a'' is the first term of an arithmetic progression and Sₙ = 2aₙ, then:","pa":"ਜੇਕਰ ਇੱਕ ਅੰਕ ਗਣਿਤਕ ਲੜੀ ਵਿੱਚ ''a'' ਪਹਿਲਾ ਪਦ ਹੈ ਅਤੇ Sₙ = 2aₙ ਹੈ, ਤਾਂ:"}', '[{"id":"a","text":{"en":"aₙ = 3a","pa":"aₙ = 3a "},"image_url":null},{"id":"b","text":{"en":"3aₙ  = na","pa":"3aₙ  = na"},"image_url":null},{"id":"c","text":{"en":"(4-n)aₙ  = na","pa":"(4-n)aₙ  = na"},"image_url":null},{"id":"d","text":{"en":"5aₙ  = a","pa":"5aₙ  = a"},"image_url":null}]', '["c"]', '{"en":"Sₙ = (n/2)(a + aₙ). Given Sn = 2aₙ. So, 2aₙ = (n/2)(a + aₙ) => 4aₙ= na + naₙ => 4aₙ - naₙ = na => aₙ(4-n) = na.","pa":"Sn = (n/2)(a + an). ਦਿੱਤਾ ਹੈ Sn = 2an. ਇਸ ਲਈ, 2an = (n/2)(a + an) => 4an = na + nan => 4an - nan = na => an(4-n) = na."}', 1, '0.00', NULL, 2, NULL, NULL, 3, NULL, '"2026-02-14T10:57:16.270Z"', '"2026-02-14T10:57:16.270Z"'),
